Pendulum Effect
 If you Special Summon a "DD" monster(s), except during the Damage Step: You can target 1 "DD" monster in your Graveyard; any battle damage your opponent takes is halved for the rest of this turn, also Special Summon it, and if you do, take 1000 damage. You can only use this effect of "DDD Abyss Ragnarok the Destruction Overlord" once per turn.

 Monster Effect
 If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can target 1 "DDD" monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon it. You can only use this effect of "DDD Abyss Ragnarok the Destruction Overlord" once per turn. Once per turn: You can Tribute 1 other "DD" monster you control, then target 1 monster your opponent controls; banish it.
